data.description: Unheard of opportunity for assumable VA loan below 3%!! If your looking for Country Living with a View...look no further! Situated on the Clarkston foothills, this amazing COMPLETELY finished home has everything you could wish for. Plenty of room on l.26 acres for an additional shop, pets, and a HUGE Garden! Comes with nice sized storage shop, an Amazing Garage with Heat and A/C, built in cabinetry. There are 2 extra large master suites, 4 FULL bathrooms, Custom Cabinetry, Large Pantry, Granite Countertops, Fantastic Storage...and more!!! Give us a call for your showing appointment and details.
